\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.5 SIR Entry Closure
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
A SIR entry closes when its linked work order or project record closes,
 or when the IT Director authorizes cancellation.
 The Assistant IT Director shall confirm closure of the SIR entry within two (2) business days of the closure event or the IT Director's cancellation authorization.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.6 Annual Improvement Summary
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The Assistant IT Director shall produce an annual improvement summary documenting:
 volume of SIR entries logged,
 entries routed to work orders,
 entries routed to projects,
 entries closed,
 and entries cancelled.
 The Assistant IT Director shall submit the summary to the IT Director as part of the 
\series bold
Policy 
